snippet.title: Oodee's Passion - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
What will it take to leave this strange land? A man and a his spirit companion must craft, explore and cooperate to survive in this split-screen adventure.

A game developed by:
David Padron-Harris &
Barry Yip

With music and sound effects by:
James Morrell &
Katie Rupinski
